  <title>
    <phrase>Keyboard Shortcuts</phrase>
  </title>
  <indexterm>
    <primary>Keyboard Shortcuts</primary>
  </indexterm>
  <para>
    The usage of this command is described in
    <xref linkend="gimp-concepts-shortcuts"/>.
  </para>
  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase>Activate the Command</phrase>
    </title>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You can access this command from the toolbox menubar through
          <menuchoice><guimenu><accel>F</accel>ile</guimenu><guimenuitem><accel>K</accel>eyboard Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice><guimenu><accel>E</accel>dit</guimenu><guimenuitem><accel>K</accel>eyboard Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
